{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三回 海上争锋。辛捷被缪七娘挟持回船，发现对方竟是无极岛主无恨生夫妇，因手帕误认他是梅山民。无恨生夫妇要将他带回无极岛，在九妹墓前杀他祭奠。张菁对辛捷心生好感，趁夜偷入暗舱为他解穴放走。辛捷逃出数丈即被无恨生追回，再遭囚禁。数日后船出长江入东海，遇玉骨魔麾下黄子沙海盗帮伏击，成一青以毒酒诱饮，海盗船炸毁无恨生座船。混战中辛捷落海，张菁冒险投木板救他穴道，二人在浪涛中相对。此时海上飓风骤起，海盗船触礁倾覆，无恨生以十指钉甲求生，生死未卜。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这厮倒狡猾得很。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "你刚才问清楚了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "text": "那手帕果然是他的，他自己也承认了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想将他带回岛上，到九妹墓前，再杀了他祭九妹，让他知道负心的结果。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "张菁",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "怎样我们又要回岛上去呀。我不来了，爹爹不是答应我到这来玩个痛快吗？现在人家什么都没有玩到，怎么就要回去厂呢？岛上那么小，烦死人了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "你说我们无极岛不好玩，天下武林中想到无极岛上来的人，不知有几千几万个呢！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "张菁",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "他们要来是他们的事，我……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "不要多讲了，你要到中原来玩，以后多的是机会，这次我们先回去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "傻孩子，你急什么，爹爹妈妈总不能一辈子将你留在岛上呀。你以后总要嫁人的，嫁了人，你就可以到处去玩了，你说是不是？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "可是呀！你以后可千万不能嫁给这种人，他姓梅，叫梅山民，你的阿姨就是给他气死的，妈妈也要杀死他，给你九阿姨报仇。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也怕死了呀。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转舵向东，我们要回去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将这个人抬到后面堆东西的舱里去，每天给他灌一点稀饭，不要让他在路上饿死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "张菁",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你快走呀！被我爹爹知道了，可不得了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你想走？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "阁下有许多事误会了，我……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "你做的好事，快跟我回舱去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "text": "我们又快到家了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "这次回到岛上，真该好好管教菁儿了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "我笑有些活得不太耐烦的海盗，要来抢我们的船了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "text": "这倒奇怪了，东海上居然还有不认识我们这艘船的海盗帮。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "不过也许不是呢！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这帮海盗排场到不小，不知道是哪一帮的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还没有看到有海盗这样抢人家东西的。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看，他们怎么穿着这种衣服？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "text": "这些人莫非是黄海'沿海十沙'的海盗，可是……绝对是了，若是东海的海盗，也不会有人来打我们这艘船的主意的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "你说他们是'金字沙'、'黄子沙'、'冷家沙'还有那些什么'大沙'、'北沙'的一大群海盗吗？听说那些海盗全被'玉骨魔'收服了，不大出黄海做案的呀，怎么会巴巴地跑到东海来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些杀人不眨眼的强盗，现在却全都一个个规规矩矩，想来一定是被那'玉骨魔'制得服服帖帖的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "喂，你知不知道这个'玉骨魔'到底是怎样一个人呀？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "text": "你还指望我知道这些妖魔小丑的来历呀。不过这个'玉骨魔'倒是像真有两下子的，能够让无极岛主说'真有两下子。'此人也差可慰了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "喂，你这些年又没有在外走动过，怎么会知道他真有两下呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "text": "我起先也不知道，前些年我们岛上管花木的老刘，到如皋去买桃花的花籽，回来时告诉我说：'黄海十沙的海盗，全都被一个叫'玉骨魔'的收服了，连当年纵横南沙的涉海金鳌庞士湛，全都被他制得服服帖帖。'我当时听了，虽然觉得奇怪，但实在也没有在意，想不到今天人家却找到我头上来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "speaker_name": "缪七娘",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "这么说来，这家伙好像真的不知道我们的底细。他从黄海辛苦地跑到东海来，难道是专来对付我们这条船的吗？那我倒要看看他到底怎样厉害。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_miao_qi_niang",
      "text": "他比你一定差远了，你要是想做强盗，怕不连南海的人都收罗了来才怪。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_yi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "成一青",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "黄子沙总舵主成一青奉命请候无极岛主俪安。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_cheng_yi_qing",
      "text": "就请成舵主回上贵帮主，我东海无极岛主久仰大名，只是无暇拜会。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_yi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "成一青",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "敝帮主曾命在下略备粗酒为岛主接风，敬请岛主过来一叙。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": "char_cheng_yi_qing",
      "text": "贵帮主美意，敝夫妇心领了，只是尚有要事必须回岛，就请阁下代向贵帮主致意。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_yi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "成一青",
      "listener": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "text": "既是如此，还待成某敬岛主夫妇一杯，略表敬意。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_yi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "成一青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拙荆不善饮酒，老夫一并饮了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请让路。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_hen_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "无恨生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鼠辈敢尔！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    }
  ],
